Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谷口那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然說要在那家便利商店打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.74,0:00:17.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前在烤肉店打工的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看上的女孩子辭職後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.50,0:00:22.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他也立刻就放手不幹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.04,0:00:25.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是沒吃夠苦頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,畢竟他是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
