Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.55,0:02:06.02,Title - 20,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(796,880)\fad(695,695)}小長門有希的消失II
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.61,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看樣子能好好讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.57,0:02:21.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:30.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,圖書館內請保持安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比我預期中的更喜歡這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.57,0:03:01.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.24,0:03:05.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.66,0:03:07.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來已經高興得手足無措了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該說是厲害的集中力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要知道她會這麼開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.42,0:03:21.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早點帶她過來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.22,0:03:26.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 喜歡看書的是現在的長門啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.27,0:03:30.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於願意停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.90,0:03:37.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 長門 我們是來讀書的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看一下就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絲毫不動搖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看她那麼開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼好意思讓她停下來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在那邊等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.60,0:04:12.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看夠了再過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.52,0:04:14.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真是的真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.05,0:04:48.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.35,0:04:50.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.10,0:04:52.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}這好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.14,0:04:53.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}啊 這什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.15,0:04:57.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.48,0:04:59.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.70,0:05:14.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉打過來的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種壓迫感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 你接了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:28.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你和長門在一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.10,0:05:31.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.43,0:05:33.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在一起的話就沒事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為她還沒回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.77,0:05:37.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有點擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.02,0:05:39.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不接電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.15,0:05:42.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還是愛操心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是辛苦啊 這位媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.41,0:05:50.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天毫無成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.99,0:05:51.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是我這邊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.54,0:05:55.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,馬上就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我現在去找長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 嗯 拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.46,0:06:07.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連教科書都沒翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害 一動不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經閉館了 回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快 把書放回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.49,0:06:35.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我看到能罷手的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.29,0:06:37.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,容我拒絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.54,0:06:38.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就再給我十分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是遺憾 十分鐘後就關門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.75,0:06:43.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就九分鐘 沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.21,0:06:46.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真會擠時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你擺出那副表情也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就快點辦張卡借走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.19,0:07:03.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.86,0:07:10.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帶了卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你帶了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.24,0:07:14.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看你那麼不願鬆手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還以為沒有帶呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.37,0:07:19.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛剛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.58,0:07:21.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才想起來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.38,0:07:25.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 那就無可厚非了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.75,0:07:28.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 那趕快借一借回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在想起來之前我都不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.89,0:07:37.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡是以前的長門有希和他的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.48,0:07:42.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初遇的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.64,0:08:17.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.57,0:08:33.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,書給我 你要辦借書卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在和你說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.08,0:08:42.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想辦借書卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.54,0:08:45.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我來幫你辦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等 等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.65,0:09:08.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 就是這個呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.28,0:09:12.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.66,0:09:17.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用不用 我反而要為擅自做主而道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.41,0:09:23.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為身邊有這種讓人操心的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我就沒辦法無視需要幫助的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.54,0:09:28.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我拿不到書啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是讓我操心的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.05,0:09:36.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.64,0:09:43.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不許這麼大聲地叫別人的外號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唔喵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不許學貓叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.23,0:09:50.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒能道謝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.84,0:10:21.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我做了個夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.93,0:10:24.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.81,0:10:24.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.52,0:10:28.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早餐的準備還需要些時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.77,0:10:31.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先去換衣服洗臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.08,0:10:50.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在夢裡 我凝視著她的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.46,0:10:55.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一點一點地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.09,0:10:58.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我體內沉睡著的她的人格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.55,0:11:01.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許在一點一點地甦醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.47,0:11:06.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果她完全甦醒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.56,0:11:09.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我 現在的這個我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.31,0:11:12.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會怎樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.99,0:11:25.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也是特價日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門就拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.42,0:11:33.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.50,0:11:37.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 我們就去圖書館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.05,0:11:40.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天一定要好好讀書呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.97,0:11:41.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.51,0:11:47.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前 有點事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 那就趕快搞定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.60,0:11:56.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係 你先去圖書館也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算我一個人去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.61,0:12:03.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會睡著 又會睡著 絕對會睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.92,0:12:18.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 是這個吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.47,0:12:29.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼樣呢 要帶著回去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.15,0:12:41.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了 那我把這個放到盒子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.61,0:12:43.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.57,0:12:46.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼鏡修好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很合適吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.47,0:13:11.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再次挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.31,0:13:18.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天要好好讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.40,0:13:23.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很在意你剛才的停頓…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.11,0:13:30.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘛 這只是我的請求而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.74,0:13:32.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然很對不起長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.33,0:13:36.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望你能在身邊幫我 陪我一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.08,0:13:39.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:41.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 這題…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.05,0:14:25.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.22,0:14:26.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.47,0:14:29.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把這個代入的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:33.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此 是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.81,0:14:35.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我懂了 謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.26,0:15:14.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有個我不會的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.23,0:15:24.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸 長門也會有不會做的問題…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.90,0:15:31.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.11,0:15:34.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我去找找有沒有什麼可以參考的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.37,0:15:37.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有不會的就立刻叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我立刻回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總覺得今天的我有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.34,0:15:58.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我要拒絕戴上她的眼鏡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.35,0:16:02.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我會對他過於關注？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.48,0:16:04.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.65,0:16:08.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這鼓動的速度會變快？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.44,0:16:13.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,數據不足 無法理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.78,0:16:19.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,契機是在夢裡看到她以前的記憶 這個沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.04,0:16:24.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的人格在漸漸的覺醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.21,0:16:31.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 我現在擁有的不可思議的感覺也是她的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.76,0:16:40.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是我 雖說我擁有她的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.97,0:16:42.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感情和感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.89,0:16:47.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在所認識的情報、經驗都是我自己的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.36,0:16:49.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這些都是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.15,0:16:53.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.49,0:16:57.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.87,0:17:02.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的意識跟我的意識混合在一起？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.46,0:17:06.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨著她覺醒的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.42,0:17:06.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隨著她覺醒的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.29,0:17:08.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:10.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.01,0:17:17.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會跟我的混在一起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 在她完全覺醒的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可能會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無法阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到那時候將會發生什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我跟她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.26,0:18:02.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門同學解不了的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖說我來幫忙有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.06,0:18:09.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但至少這種小事我能幫上忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.48,0:18:14.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拿好 你的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真是多管閒事 褒義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還好是褒義的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,「我只是自己看不下去而已」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊對對對 就是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.75,0:18:35.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸？我有跟你說過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.64,0:18:41.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.64,0:18:49.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺好像久違的看到長門的微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.60,0:18:51.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欸 這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.74,0:19:01.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概是加上那時候的那份感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.03,0:19:03.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候？哪個時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.24,0:19:04.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.75,0:19:10.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.46,0:19:17.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 先趁熱來一塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要現在吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.84,0:19:58.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊不 不是不可以 不是不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.55,0:20:02.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.97,0:20:04.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.93,0:20:08.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請慢吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,僅僅是呆呆地觀望著他們的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,單純的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.41,0:20:26.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,單純的…夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.21,0:20:36.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是魔法什麼的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.18,0:20:46.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺能摸到 卻又摸不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.10,0:22:20.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛剛那個是我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.77,0:22:27.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說 她的人格照這樣慢慢地覺醒的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.03,0:22:31.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會…我會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.87,0:22:34.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
